      "content": "flying fatigue syndrome?? i haven't heard of that. it feels a bit more weird than just being tired tho, like my left side just feels... off. but if you think it's just the dehydration and the flight, i guess i'll just wait it out. you think i should take anything for it? maybe some ibuprofen or something to help me sleep?",
